<MainLayout title="Advocacy | Corrine J Blackthorn">
<section><div class="container"><div class="section-heading"><span class="kicker">Advocacy</span><h1>Fighting for people who are pushed aside.</h1><p>I believe compassion is action. My advocacy focuses on people who are often ignored, excluded, or left behind.</p></div><div class="grid"><article class="card"><h3>Trans Rights</h3><p>Visibility, dignity, safety, and equal access.</p></article><article class="card"><h3>Disability Rights</h3><p>Accessibility, accommodation, inclusion, and respect.</p></article><article class="card"><h3>Homelessness</h3><p>No one should be discarded by society. Everyone deserves safety and support.</p></article></div></div></section><section class="quote-band"><div class="container"><blockquote>I want to be remembered as someone who fought for those who couldn't fight for themselves.</blockquote></div></section></MainLayout>